webhooks.description:
Send this object as another transactional notification option. If you have a **Webhook** configured through the Console, notifications will be sent to both the **API** and **Console** channels — they are not mutually exclusive.

Notifications appear in the Webhooks Notifications dashboard with a `Configuration` field identifying the source.

**Example:**
```json
{
  "webhooks": [
    {
      "events": ["approvedTransaction", "declinedTransaction"],
      "headers": [{"label": "json", "value": "12"}],
      "urls": ["https://your-endpoint.example.com"]
    }
  ]
}
```

